Bundled snippets
================================================================================

Most snippet files under src/main/resources/com/editora/snippets/ (the
VS Code-format *.json files for C, C++, C#, CSS, Go, HTML, Java, Kotlin,
Markdown, PowerShell, Python, Ruby, Rust, shell, and SQL) are taken from the
"friendly-snippets" collection and redistributed under the MIT License:

    friendly-snippets — https://github.com/rafamadriz/friendly-snippets
    Copyright (c) 2021 Rafael Madriz
    License: MIT

The core language files are vendored unmodified (framework-specific extras are
not included). The remaining snippet files (xml, batchfile, groovy, json, yaml,
ini, global) are original to Editora and covered by Editora's own MIT License.

